original_title: Get Your Body Back: One Hour Yoga with Myra Shaikh
overview: In this 1 Hour Yoga class you will get a all in one routine, strength, tone & flexibility. Yoga instructor Myra Shakih does a beginner level workout flow. This class is great for women & men of all ages!
tagline: A one hour yoga workout routine, that covers stretching, toning & strengthening
title: Get Your Body Back: One Hour Yoga with Myra Shaikh
